# Smart Troubleshooting API — Frontend

Base URL (local dev): `http://127.0.0.1:8000` — webpack proxies `/api/fleets` and `/api/troubleshoot` to FastAPI alongside logs.

All HTTP in `client/src/services/troubleshootService.ts`. TanStack Query in `client/src/hooks/troubleshoot/`.

## Endpoints

| Method | Path | When |
|--------|------|------|
| GET | `/api/fleets/dropdown` | Page mount — populate aircraft dropdown |
| POST | `/api/troubleshoot` | User submits fault description |

### Fleet dropdown response (200)

```json
[
  { "id": "uuid-111", "tail_number": "N901VA" },
  { "id": "uuid-222", "tail_number": "N902VA" }
]
```

### Troubleshoot request body

```json
{
  "fleet_id": "uuid-111",
  "fault_description": "Transponder intermittent on climb..."
}
```

### Troubleshoot response (200)

```json
{
  "summary": {
    "root_cause_discovery": "...",
    "recommended_action": "...",
    "estimated_fix_time_mins": 45,
    "historical_average_mins": 240,
    "suggested_part_number": "#XYZ-123"
  },
  "historical_matches": [
    {
      "id": "res-uuid",
      "action_taken": "Cleaned corroded connector pins on plug P3.",
      "labor_minutes": 45
    }
  ]
}
```

## TypeScript (troubleshootService.ts)

- `FleetDropdownItem` — `{ id, tail_number }`
- `TroubleshootRequest` — `{ fleet_id, fault_description }`
- `TroubleshootResponse` — `{ summary, historical_matches }`
- `formatDuration(mins)` — display helper for fix-time badges
- `validateTroubleshootRequest()` — client-side guard before POST
- `parseFastApiError()` — reused from `logService.ts`

## UI

- Route: `/troubleshoot` — `TroubleshootPage` with in-page dashboard sidebar
- Fleet selection: `SelectField` (native `<select>`), not `SelectBox`
- Fault input: shared `TextArea`
- Loading: shared `Spinner` during POST (~2s backend lag)
- Results: `RootCauseCard`, `SuggestedPartNumber`, `FixTimeComparisonBadge`, `HistoricalMatchesList`

## Errors

FastAPI: `{ "detail": "message" }` or validation array. Use `parseFastApiError`.
